where ${U_{ij}}$ is the line $i$ , column $j$ element of the unitary matrix $U$ .

Based on the above definition , the amplitude distribution of person 's state evolves to $\psi \left( t \right)$ from the initial $\psi \left( 0 \right)$ across time $t$ as Eq. ( \ref{psit_new} ) , which shows the dynamic in a decision making process .
\begin{equation}\label{psit_new}
\psi \left( t \right) = U \cdot \psi \left( 0 \right)
\end{equation}

